      • Airline

        public Airline(java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String alias,
               java.lang.String iata,
               java.lang.String icao,
               java.lang.String callSign,
               java.lang.String country,
               boolean active)
        Creates a new airline.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the airline
        alias - alias the airline flies under
        iata - 2-letter IATA (International Air Transport Association) code
        icao - 3-letter ICAO (International Civil Aviation Organization) code
        callSign - airline's call sign
        country - country or territory where airline is incorporated
        active - true if the airline is or has until recently been operational, false if it is defunct.
